## 6. Why AI Exists (The Real Reason)

AI exists because:
- Humans cannot process massive data
- Patterns are hidden inside large datasets
- Decisions must be fast and scalable

### Real-world uses:
- Google Maps â†’ traffic prediction
- Netflix â†’ movie recommendations
- Banks â†’ fraud detection
- Hospitals â†’ disease diagnosis
- Chatbots â†’ language understanding

All of these use the same AI principle.

